 <p id="Par54" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">We define 
  <div id="IEq34" class="inline-formula">
   <div class="alternatives">
    <span id="M83" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ \hat{V}_{L}^{A} (K,L) \equiv V_{\pi }^{A} \left( {K - L,\varPi (L)} \right)\varPi^{\prime } (L) - V_{K - L}^{A} \left( {K - L,\varPi (L)} \right) &gt; 0 $$\end{document}</span>
